I won't even debate the humanity of the fetus, since I don't think people should get abortions in the majority of situations.  Making abortions illegal will not make them go away.  It will only drive  them underground, making the procedure unsafe.  It will force people who are in no way ready or willing to be parents to become parents.  Forcing that situation would only serve to cause more suffering for the child.  Why force a child to live with someone who obviously has no desire for it to be around.  Situations like that are just begging for abuse.  <br>
<br>
